title: 11/20: Waiver Wire, KC-LAR Thoughts (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
What a game! And what a week for the Waiver Wire! Who are our top priorities (2:00)? Are Gus Edwards and Josh Adams ready to take over in their respective backfields? Which rookie WRs do we like? ... How much FAAB are we spending (5:25)? News and notes (13:53), a sneak peak at the Waiver Wire for each position (17:00), CHI-MIN (28:40) and KC-LAR (34:50) recaps. What's going on with Dalvin Cook and do we trust the Rams TEs going forward? ... Waiver Wire QBs (40:00) including Jameis Winston and Lamar Jackson, RBs (44:48) including Elijah McGuire and Theo Riddick, WRs (48:40) including DJ Moore and Tre'Quan Smith among many others, TEs (57:30) including Cameron Brate and Ben Watson plus DSTs and Kickers ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
